Jamaica Ave., at the S.W. corner of 78th Street (formerly Snedeker Ave.), showing the Thos. Snedeker honasof 1860. 0ther owners were C. Vanderveer, 1873; and C.B. Vanderveer in 1891.
It was demolished in 1924.
